1
00:00:00,250 --> 00:00:02,166
Name: Rayan Riyad Khalil

2
00:00:03,208 --> 00:00:04,875
Born in 1987

3
00:00:06,125 --> 00:00:08,583
My clan is al-Sabaawi

4
00:00:09,708 --> 00:00:11,750
By God, our—my situation

5
00:00:13,083 --> 00:00:14,750
I was a driver on the Turkey route

6
00:00:15,958 --> 00:00:17,833
We took people and brought others

7
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:20,250
And in the meantime

8
00:00:21,291 --> 00:00:22,375
I started having problems

9
00:00:22,416 --> 00:00:24,250
They started monitoring us, and so on

10
00:00:24,416 --> 00:00:25,666
And because of that our situation got worse

11
00:00:25,958 --> 00:00:29,125
The route was closed, and we had a shop in Ras al-Kour

12
00:00:29,791 --> 00:00:33,291
It was a barbershop belonging to my brothers

13
00:00:33,916 --> 00:00:36,666
Being there meant I didn’t have a job

14
00:00:37,166 --> 00:00:42,083
We started transporting people and taking them to…

15
00:00:42,833 --> 00:00:47,000
We took them from here to Raqqa, and from Raqqa they went to Turkey

16
00:00:47,916 --> 00:00:49,000
And during this time

17
00:00:49,500 --> 00:00:52,666
Once or twice I was caught, and so on

18
00:00:53,416 --> 00:00:55,291
So I was being watched closely

19
00:00:57,166 --> 00:01:00,125
They kept following me a lot, I was under surveillance

20
00:01:00,875 --> 00:01:02,291
I felt I was being watched
